			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">31.205-34</ph> Recruitment costs.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d1964e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1978e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Subject to paragraph (b) of this subsection, the following costs are allowable:</p>
					          <ol id="d1964e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1978e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Costs of help-wanted advertising.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1978e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Costs of operating an employment office needed to secure and maintain an adequate labor force.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1978e45" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Costs of operating an aptitude and educational testing program.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1978e54" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Travel costs of employees engaged in recruiting personnel.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1978e63" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Travel costs of applicants for interviews.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1978e73" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(6)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Costs for employment agencies, not in excess of standard commercial rates.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d1978e84" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
